---
title: Sticky Ginger Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Salad with Sesame Dressing
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve enlisted the help of a lively glaze made with ginger, soy sauce and honey: it coats each bite of tender chicken breast in sticky, salty sweetness and pairs perfectly with the sesame dressing that's drizzled over the robust roast pumpkin salad. Go for your life!
